This is the source code file:
driver/driver.java		// The main file, you can run the routine in this file

exception/Overrecordnum.java	// The exception, would throw when the number of record 				// over 40
model/Student.java		// The student class file. 	

Util/Display.java		// A abstract class, would be extended by 						// DisplayStudentclass

Util/DisplayStudent.java	// a class extends Display class, it can print all 					// information about student

Util/Printstatis.java		// interface, support other class print statistic 					// information function

Util/Statistics.java		// compute the highest, lowest and average scores from 					// record

Util/Util.java			// read record from .txt file and extends DisplayStduent 				// class, so that it also can print all information.